item.title: Bootstrapping macOS workspace
item.description: I have experienced a number of different Mac systems, ranging from the old white MacBook 2006 to iMac and MacMini 2010 and lately MacBook Pro 13” and 15”. Time Machine has helped me a lot to transfer data from the old to the new machine.
